('award_introduction', '<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; outline: none; color: #555555; font-family: open_sansregular;\"><span style=\"color: #555555; font-family: open_sansregular;\">最佳新西蘭葡萄酒的目的地，位於卡馬爾頓&middot;戈爾路104號紐馬克特。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; outline: none; color: #555555; font-family: open_sansregular;\"><span style=\"color: #555555; font-family: open_sansregular;\">酒窖的名字來源於法國的&ldquo; la Cave&rdquo;，意為&ldquo;酒窖&rdquo;。 當您進入我們的商店時，您很快就會沉浸在我們經過結構設計的酒窖貨架中，展示著500多種來自NZ精品店/單一葡萄園和手工烈酒的頂級葡萄酒。 加入我們的品嚐室，或在la Cave旁坐下，享受多達16種葡萄酒，或在我們精選的精品酒莊或有機葡萄園中挑選葡萄酒中的一瓶。</span></p>', '2020-05-28 04:24:33'),
('award_introduction_en', '<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; outline: none; color: #555555; font-family: open_sansregular;\"><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: arial, sans-serif;\">The destination of best New Zealand wines, located at 104 Carlton Gore Road Newmarket. </span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; outline: none; color: #555555; font-family: open_sansregular;\"><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: arial, sans-serif;\">The Wine Cave\'s name is derived from the French \'la cave\', meaning \'of cellar\'. As you enter our store that you are soon immersed in our architecturally designed wine cellar shelves displaying over 500 top quality wines from NZ boutique/single vineyard &amp; handcraft spirits. Join us at our Tasting Room or have a seat next to our la Cave, enjoy up to 16 wines or open a bottle among our selection of wines from boutique wineries or or organic approached vineyards.</span></p>', '2020-05-28 04:24:33'),
('corporate_image', 'file-manager\\corporate-wine-service.jpg', '2020-05-28 04:22:17'),
('corporate_introduction', '<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; outline: none; color: #555555; font-family: open_sansregular;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; vertical-align: inherit;\">您的公司中是否有需要酒的常規職能？</span><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; vertical-align: inherit;\">還是您想與客戶保持慷慨，不時向他們發送禮物？</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; outline: none; color: #555555; font-family: open_sansregular;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; vertical-align: inherit;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; vertical-align: inherit;\">讓我們為您的企業安排定期的葡萄酒配送，為您的辛勞工作打好基礎。</span><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; vertical-align: inherit;\">我們可以根據您的口味，當然還有您的需求和預算來定制您的訂單。</span><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; vertical-align: inherit;\">可以根據您的喜好安排每週，每兩週或每月交貨。</span><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; vertical-align: inherit;\">您永遠都不會用完適合自己口味的好酒，當您給他們送去一大杯時，您的客戶將不勝感激。</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; outline: none; color: #555555; font-family: open_sansregular;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; vertical-align: inherit;\">現在就聯繫我們，我們將與您聯繫討論您的要求。</span></p>\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; font-size: 18px; font-weight: normal; color: #555555; font-family: open_sansregular; line-height: 20px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none;\">我們需要一個帳戶來從 The Wine Cave 訂購嗎？</strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; outline: none; color: #555555; font-family: open_sansregular;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; vertical-align: inherit;\">當您在我們這裡創建帳戶時，它會帶來一系列好處： </span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none;\" /><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; vertical-align: inherit;\">&bull;加快結帳速度 </span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none;\" /><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; vertical-align: inherit;\">&bull;訪問過往訂單</span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none;\" /><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; vertical-align: inherit;\"> &bull;付款明細方便存儲 </span></p>\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; font-size: 18px; font-weight: normal; color: #555555; font-family: open_sansregular; line-height: 20px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none;\">我們可以創建一個信用帳戶嗎？</strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; outline: none; color: #555555; font-family: open_sansregular;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; vertical-align: inherit;\">如果您想在 The Wine Cave 建立商業信用帳戶，請致電09 930 8115。我們需要知道您是否是現有客戶。</span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none;\" /><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; vertical-align: inherit;\">&bull;業務類型（例如，獨家貿易公司，慈善公司等） </span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none;\" /><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; vertical-align: inherit;\">&bull;付款明細</span></p>', '2020-05-28 04:22:17'),
('corporate_introduction_en', '<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; outline: none; color: #555555; font-family: open_sansregular;\">Do you have regular functions within your business that require wine? Or maybe you like to be generous with your clients and send them a gift once in a while?</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; outline: none; color: #555555; font-family: open_sansregular;\">Let us take care of the hard work for you by arranging a regular wine delivery to your business. We can customize your order to suit your tastes, and of course your needs and any budget. Weekly, fortnightly or monthly deliveries can be arranged based on your preference. You need never run out of good wine to suit your taste, and your clients will be very grateful when you send them a great drop.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; outline: none; color: #555555; font-family: open_sansregular;\">Simply contact us now and we\'ll be in touch to discuss your requirements.</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; font-size: 18px; font-weight: normal; color: #555555; font-family: open_sansregular; line-height: 20px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none;\">Do we need an account to order from The Wine Cave?</strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; outline: none; color: #555555; font-family: open_sansregular;\">When you create an account with us it comes with a range of benefits: <br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none;\" />&bull; speedier checkout <br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none;\" />&bull; access to past orders<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none;\" /> &bull; payment details conveniently stored </p>\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none; font-size: 18px; font-weight: normal; color: #555555; font-family: open_sansregular; line-height: 20px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none;\">Can we create a credit account?</strong></h3>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; outline: none; color: #555555; font-family: open_sansregular;\">If you wish to set up a business credit account with The Wine Cave please call us on 09 930 8115. We\'ll need to know whether you are an existing customer or not.<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none;\" />&bull; Type of business (eg Sole trader, Ltd company, Charity etc) <br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none;\" />&bull; Payment details</p>', '2020-05-28 04:22:17');
