('ByyG1600756383Hpqr', 'file-manager/酒類/620819c2aa3564daf3c6f429a282d59.png', 'file-manager/酒類/620819c2aa3564daf3c6f429a282d59.png', 'file-manager/酒類/620819c2aa3564daf3c6f429a282d59.png', 'Rosé + Sauvignon Blanc + Pinot Noir', 'Rosé + Sauvignon Blanc + Pinot Noir', 90, '', 750, 13, 1, 1, 4, 1, 'NZ', 2, 2, 'null', NULL, NULL, 100, '2020-09-22', NULL, 1, 4, 0, 0, 0, NULL, '<p>长相思：</p>\r\n<p>风味</p>\r\n<p>经典的马尔堡（Marlborough），我们的2018年长相思（Sauvignon blanc）具有成熟的西番莲果，酸橙和葡萄柚味。</p>\r\n<p>口感</p>\r\n<p>丰富而复杂，果核密集。柑橘和热带水果的多层口味使它成为极佳的葡萄酒。这些风味和香气在口感上留下新鲜的余韵，使它成为平衡酸度的令人满意的葡萄酒。</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>黑皮诺：</p>\r\n<p>风味</p>\r\n<p>这款优雅的果味黑松露葡萄酒具有丰富的李子和樱桃特征，在鼻子中散发出些许野生树莓的香气。</p>\r\n<p>口感</p>\r\n<p>淡淡的泥土味将这些香气联系在一起，并伴随着微妙的黑胡椒香料和刨花延续到味蕾上。这是一款中等重量的皮诺，单宁含量高，可以延长酒体的使用寿命。</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Rose：</p>\r\n<p>风味</p>\r\n<p>这款充满活力的玫瑰提供草莓，樱桃和奶油苏打味。明亮，花香和新鲜。</p>\r\n<p>口感</p>\r\n<p>轻盈多汁。酒体干爽，口感清新，果香浓郁。</p>', '<p>我们在整个新西兰以及海外一些地区提供服务。 我们的送货是由我们自己和值得信赖的第三方快递员完成的。 有关价格和送货方式的更多详细信息，请转到我们网站的&ldquo;送货&rdquo;部分。</p>', NULL, '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-NZ\">Sauvignon Blanc:</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-NZ\">NOSE</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-NZ\">Classically Marlborough, our 2018 Sauvignon blanc shows ripe passionfruit, lime, and grapefruit notes. </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-NZ\">PALATE</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-NZ\">Rich and complex with a dense fruit core. The multi-layered palate of citrus and tropical fruits make this an excellent wine to enjoy. These flavors and aromas leave a fresh lingering finish on the palate making it a full satisfying wine with balanced acidity.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-NZ\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-NZ\">Pinot Noir:</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-NZ\">NOSE</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-NZ\">This elegant fruit-forward pinot has rich plum and cherry characteristics dominating the nose with hints of wild raspberry coming through underneath. </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-NZ\">PALATE</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-NZ\">A lovely light earthiness ties these aromas all together and continues onto the palate along with subtle black pepper spice and wood shavings. This is a mid-weight Pinot with well-integrated tannins carrying through to an extended finish.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-NZ\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-NZ\">Rose:</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-NZ\">NOSE</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\">This vibrant Rose offers strawberry, cherry, and creaming soda characters. Bright, floral and fresh. </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\">PALATE</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-ansi-language: EN-US;\">Light and juicy. Dry in style, with a vibrant palette that&rsquo;s fresh and fruitily spiced.</span></p>', '<p><span style=\"color: #808080; font-family: Calibri, \'Segoe UI\', Calibri, Thonburi, Arial, Verdana, sans-serif, \'Mongolian Baiti\', \'Microsoft Yi Baiti\', \'Javanese Text\'; font-size: 16px; white-space: pre-wrap;\">We deliver throughout New Zealand and to some locations overseas. Our deliveries are made by ourselves and trusted third party couriers. For further details on prices and delivery options please go to the DELIVERY section of our website.</span></p>', 1, '', '2020-09-22 14:33:03', '2020-10-10 07:53:21'),
('cbhF1582730674jBLw', 'file-manager/wine/MAZURAN\'S.png', '', '', 'Mazuran\'s Medium Sweet Sherry', 'Mazuran\'s Medium Sweet Sherry', 45, '', 750, 19, 1, 3, 33, 1, 'NZ', 25, 2, '[\"6\",\"7\",\"8\"]', NULL, NULL, 12, '2020-02-26', '2021-02-26', 0, 124, 1, 0, 0, NULL, '<p>这款超级奶油是新西兰雪利酒之王，是30年混合的amontillado，淡琥珀色。 新鲜的酸度，柑橘味，橘皮和果酱。 在法国橡木桶中陈酿，享受冷藏。</p>', '<p>我们在整个新西兰以及海外一些地区提供服务。 我们的送货是由我们自己和值得信赖的第三方快递员完成的。 有关价格和送货方式的更多详细信息，请转到我们网站的&ldquo;送货&rdquo;部分。</p>', NULL, '<p>The king of New Zealand sherry, this mega cream is a 30 year blended amontillado, light amber brown. Fresh acidity, citrusy flavours, orange peel, and marmalade. Aged in French oak, enjoy chilled.</p>', '<p>We deliver throughout New Zealand and to some locations overseas. Our deliveries are made by ourselves and trusted third party couriers. For further details on prices and delivery options please go to DELIVERY section of our website.</p>', 1, '', '2020-02-26 23:24:34', '2020-10-19 18:09:44'),
