('dcVY1582730676qusG', 'file-manager/wine/Stonyridge larose.png', '', '', 'Stonyridge Larose 2009', 'Stonyridge Larose 2009', 360, '', 750, 13.5, 1, 1, 15, 1, 'NZ', 16, 2, '[\"7\",\"8\",\"9\"]', NULL, NULL, 12, '2020-02-26', '2021-02-26', 0, 174, 1, 0, 0, '“Stonyridge Larose – 94+ Points”', '<p>Stonyridge Vineyard的构思和运营完全旨在生产世界一流的波尔多风格的红酒。 这种经典的以赤霞珠为主的混合酒被命名为Larose，以向玫瑰致敬，玫瑰是所有花朵中最芳香，最鲜艳，最浓郁且最美丽的玫瑰。</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>葡萄园地点是专门用来生产这种风格的葡萄酒的。 葡萄园的朝北平缓坡度被山脊掩盖，免受西南偏冷的风吹，使葡萄园得名。 夏季温度通常超过30&deg;C，最高温度为36&deg;C。 结合朝北的行和出色的葡萄栽培技术，葡萄在正常年份可以达到完美的成熟度。</p>', '<p>我们在整个新西兰以及海外一些地区提供服务。 我们的送货是由我们自己和值得信赖的第三方快递员完成的。 有关价格和送货方式的更多详细信息，请转到我们网站的&ldquo;送货&rdquo;部分。</p>', '“Stonyridge Larose – 94+ Points”', '<p>Stonyridge Vineyard was conceived and operated with the sole intention of making world-class Bordeaux-style red wine. This classic Cabernet-dominant blend is named Larose as a tribute to the rose, the most aromatic, colorful, intense, and beautiful of all flowers.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>The vineyard site was chosen specifically to produce this style of wine. The gentle north-facing slopes of the vineyard are sheltered from the cold southwesterly winds by the ridge which gives the vineyard its name. Summer temperatures regularly reach over 30&deg;C with the highest temperature being 36&deg;C. Combined with north-facing rows and excellent viticulture, the grapes achieve perfect ripeness in normal years.</p>', '<p>We deliver throughout New Zealand and to some locations overseas. Our deliveries are made by ourselves and trusted third party couriers. For further details on prices and delivery options please go to DELIVERY section of our website.</p>', 1, '', '2020-02-26 23:24:36', '2020-10-19 17:51:35'),
