('Fzfm1582730676JXPS', 'file-manager/wine/beure.png', '', '', 'Stettener Riesling Trocken Schilfsandstein 2014', '', 49, '', 750, 11.5, 2, 2, 22, 2, 'DE', 33, 1, '[\"3\",\"10\",\"12\"]', NULL, NULL, 12, '2020-02-26', '2021-02-26', 0, 167, 1, 0, 0, '这款精心编织的单点葡萄酒很好地介绍了Weingut Beurer的相关风格', '<p>Stettener Riesling Schilfsandstein干酒来自StettenerPulverm&auml;cher所在地，超过35年的葡萄藤深深植根于长达2亿年的骨骼芦苇砂岩土壤中，土壤遍布石膏keuper，硅石砂岩和客厅砂岩。该地区的特点是通风良好，葡萄藤不断减产，并根据严格的生态准则耕种土壤。葡萄园自己的酵母在不锈钢中进行的自然工作和针对特定土壤的扩展产生了具有强烈特征的独特雷司令。 Beurer酒厂的土壤，多风的地理位置和自然的经济状况为Stettener Riesling芦苇砂岩提供了新鲜的多层水果，其微妙的酸度和令人陶醉的矿物质将其夹在味蕾上。这种Stettener Riesling干芦苇砂岩毫无疑问是Beurer，并且巧妙地反映了其风土特征。为了精确地保持这种个性，将VDP.Ortsriesling带入瓶中，采用了无味，安全和耐用的瓶盖。</p>', '<p>我们在整个新西兰以及海外一些地区提供服务。 我们的送货是由我们自己和值得信赖的第三方快递员完成的。 有关价格和送货方式的更多详细信息，请转到我们网站的&ldquo;送货&rdquo;部分。</p>', 'This finely woven single site wine is a good introduction to the biodynamic work of Weingut Beurer.', '<p>The Stettener Riesling Schilfsandstein dry comes from the location of the Stettener&nbsp;Pulverm&auml;cher, where the over 35 year old vines are deeply rooted in the up to 200 million year old, skeletal reed sandstone soil, which is pervaded by gypsum keuper, silica sandstone and parlor sandstone. The location is characterized by good ventilation, the vines are subjected to consistent yield reductions and the soil is cultivated according to strict ecological guidelines. The natural work and the soil-specific expansion with the vineyard\'s own yeast in stainless steel resulted in a distinctive Riesling with a strong character. The soil, the windy location and the natural economy of the Beurer winery gave the Stettener Riesling reed sandstone a fresh, multi-layered fruit, which is caught on the palate by a delicate acidity and a gripping minerality. This Stettener Riesling dry reed sandstone is unmistakably Beurer and skilfully reflects the character of its terroir. In order to preserve precisely this individuality, the VDP.Ortsriesling was brought to the bottle with a tasteless, safe and durable closure.</p>', '<p>We deliver throughout New Zealand and to some locations overseas. Our deliveries are made by ourselves and trusted third party couriers. For further details on prices and delivery options please go to DELIVERY section of our website.</p>', 1, '', '2020-02-26 23:24:36', '2020-10-21 11:10:16'),
