('GkuG1582730670jpZB', 'file-manager/wine/圣诞礼盒/未命名_自定义cm_2020-11-16-0 (3).png', '', '', 'Clearview Endeavour Chardonnay 2018', '', 200, '', 750, 14, 2, 2, 2, 2, 'NZ', 2, 2, '[\"3\",\"4\",\"5\"]', NULL, NULL, 6, '2020-02-26', '2021-02-26', 0, 20, 1, 1, 0, 'The nose is immensely voluminous with deeply concentrated with integrated and complex-layered aromas of ripe yellow stonefruits along with nutty and mealy notes, creamy barrel-ferment elements and fresh mineral and flinty detail. Medium-full bodied, the palate is extremely well-packed and concentrated with rich and luscious flavours of yellow stonefruits, savoury citrus fruits and layers of nutty and mealy elements with complexing mineral and flinty characters.', '<p>Clearview Estate Winery Ltd was established for the first red wine vintage in 1989, following some experimentation in prior years. Chardonnay began in 1991 with the release of the first Reserve Chardonnay. The vineyards have a variety of soil types and micro climates which give us the ability to capture the different elements and nuances of each particular site to produce wines of complexity and character. Each grape variety has been carefully matched to the varying soil types, ranging from beach shingle to clay producing a range of flavour profiles unique to our terroir.&nbsp;</p>', '<p>We deliver throughout New Zealand and to some locations overseas. Our deliveries are made by ourselves and trusted third party couriers. For further details on prices and delivery options please go to DELIVERY section of our website.</p>', 'The nose is immensely voluminous with deeply concentrated with integrated and complex-layered aromas of ripe yellow stonefruits along with nutty and mealy notes, creamy barrel-ferment elements and fresh mineral and flinty detail. Medium-full bodied, the palate is extremely well-packed and concentrated with rich and luscious flavours of yellow stonefruits, savoury citrus fruits and layers of nutty and mealy elements with complexing mineral and flinty characters.', '<p>Clearview Estate Winery Ltd was established for the first red wine vintage in 1989, following some experimentation in prior years. Chardonnay began in 1991 with the release of the first Reserve Chardonnay. The vineyards have a variety of soil types and micro climates which give us the ability to capture the different elements and nuances of each particular site to produce wines of complexity and character. Each grape variety has been carefully matched to the varying soil types, ranging from beach shingle to clay producing a range of flavour profiles unique to our terroir.&nbsp;</p>', NULL, 1, 'file-manager/PDF/PDF/Clearview Endeavour Chardonnay 2015.pdf', '2020-02-26 23:24:30', '2020-11-16 17:52:14'),
