ake Dunstan where Te Kano Estate is located.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-NZ\">Te Kano Estate comprises three vineyards, Northburn, &lsquo;Jerome&rsquo; in Bannockburn and &lsquo;Eliza&rsquo; in Bannockburn. Te Kano Estate is always after the very best expression of site and climate which is called &lsquo;Terroir&rsquo; . A hand selection from vineyards and barrels is a must as what they emphasize is always the Quality, not the Quantity.</span></p>', '<p>We deliver throughout New Zealand and to some locations overseas. Our deliveries are made by ourselves and trusted third party couriers. For further details on prices and delivery options please go to DELIVERY section of our website.</p>', 1, '', '2020-10-27 11:15:01', '2021-01-07 10:11:04'),
