('HRGt1582730674BYXh', 'file-manager/wine/mondillo riesling.png', '', '', 'Mondillo Riesling 2019', 'Mondillo Riesling 2019', 29, '', 750, 12.5, 2, 2, 22, 2, 'NZ', 9, 1, '[\"3\",\"5\",\"10\"]', NULL, NULL, 12, '2020-02-26', '2021-02-26', 0, 129, 1, 0, 0, '在本迪戈（Bendigo）庄园种植的2019年份酒清新而饱满，散发着年轻，成熟，桃红色，略带石灰的味道，显示出良好的强度，并略带干脆的口感。', '<p>浓郁的桃子，柑橘，蜂蜜和花果香气。柔和浓缩的葡萄酒，完美平衡，苹果味回味绵长。请享用！</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>妮娜（Nina）含有100％的雷司令（Riesling）水果，并且仅在天然葡萄孢菌出现的年份产生。每个葡萄串都经过精心挑选和手工采摘，以确保选择了最好的葡萄孢属浆果。</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>春季凉爽后，我们的2019年份含有受葡萄孢属侵染的水果，降雨量超过平均水平，随后是较长的温暖夏季，导致受浓缩葡萄的产量低，这是受到葡萄孢菌影响的水果的60％。等待了很长的时间，直到葡萄孢菌出现，5月中旬才人工采摘了妮娜的果实。这种酒只有少量可用：980瓶。</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Alc：9.8％，RS：147g / l，TA：7.5，pH：3.15</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>我们的&ldquo;妮娜&rdquo;晚丰收雷司令的名字是为了向多梅尼奇的已故母亲乔瓦尼娜（Giovanina）致敬。亲切地称为&ldquo;尼娜&rdquo;。</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>酒窖：即日起至2025年</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>服务与软奶酪，甜点一起冷藏，作为开胃酒或甜点！</p>', '<p>我们在整个新西兰以及海外一些地区提供服务。 我们的送货是由我们自己和值得信赖的第三方快递员完成的。 有关价格和送货方式的更多详细信息，请转到我们网站的&ldquo;送货&rdquo;部分。</p>', 'Estate-grown at Bendigo, the 2019 vintage is fresh and full bodiesd with youthful ripe, peachy, slightly limey flavours, showing good intensity, and a slightly off-dry crisp finish.', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 9px; hyphens: none; color: #808080; font-size: 16px; padding-top: 15px; line-height: 28px; font-family: palatino !important;\">Concentrated aromas of peach, citrus, honey and floral fruits. A softly concentrated wine, perfectly balanced, with a lingering apple finish. Enjoy!</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 9px; hyphens: none; color: #808080; font-size: 16px; padding-top: 15px; line-height: 28px; font-family: palatino !important;\">Nina contains 100% Riesling fruit, and is only produced in years that natural botrytis occurs. Each grape cluster is carefully chosen and picked by hand to ensure that the best botrytis berries are selected.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 9px; hyphens: none; color: #808080; font-size: 16px; padding-top: 15px; line-height: 28px; font-family: palatino !important;\">Our 2019 vintage contains 60% botrytis affected fruit after a cool spring, with above average rainfall, followed by a long warm summer which produced low yields of concentrated fruit. It was a long wait until the botrytis set in and the Nina fruit was hand-picked mid-May. Only a small amount of this wine is available: 980 bottles.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 9px; hyphens: none; color: #808080; font-size: 16px; padding-top: 15px; line-height: 28px; font-family: palatino !important;\">Alc: 9.8%, RS: 147 g/l, TA: 7.5, pH: 3.15</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 9px; hyphens: none; color: #808080; font-size: 16px; padding-top: 15px; line-height: 28px; font-family: palatino !important;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 9px; hyphens: none; color: #808080; font-size: 16px; padding-top: 15px; line-height: 28px; font-family: palatino !important;\">Our &lsquo;Nina&rsquo; Late Harvest Riesling is named in tribute to Domenic&rsquo;s late mother Giovanina - a wonderfully sweet Italian lady; affectionately referred to as &lsquo;Nina&rsquo;.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 9px; hyphens: none; color: #808080; font-size: 16px; padding-top: 15px; line-height: 28px; font-family: palatino !important;\">Drink/Cellar: Now until 2025</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 9px; hyphens: none; color: #808080; font-size: 16px; padding-top: 15px; line-height: 28px; font-family: palatino !important;\">Serve chilled with soft cheeses, dessert, as an aperitif or as dessert!</p>', '<p>We deliver throughout New Zealand and to some locations overseas. Our deliveries are made by ourselves and trusted third party couriers. For further details on prices and delivery options please go to DELIVERY section of our website.</p>', 1, '', '2020-02-26 23:24:34', '2020-10-21 12:33:40'),
