es through maturation to maintain freshness while having purity, elegance and structure.</span></p>', '<p>We deliver throughout New Zealand and to some locations overseas. Our deliveries are made by ourselves and trusted third party couriers. For further details on prices and delivery options please go to DELIVERY section of our website.</p>', 1, '', '2020-02-26 23:24:30', '2020-10-27 15:58:30'),
('mOaI1582730677mRNY', 'file-manager/wine/The Chocolate Block.png', '', '', 'Boekenhoutskloof The Chocolate Block 2015', 'Boekenhoutskloof The Chocolate Block 2015', 54, '', 750, 14, 1, 1, 8, 1, '', 35, 2, '[\"8\",\"9\"]', NULL, NULL, 12, '2020-02-26', '2021-02-26', 0, 188, 1, 0, 0, NULL, '<p>2015年的葡萄酒混合了71％的西拉，15％的歌海娜，8％的赤霞珠，5％的Cinsault和单一的Viognier。西拉，歌海娜和辛索的很大一部分现在都从我们自己的葡萄园中消失了，这些葡萄园是波森兰伯格和金矿的腐烂片岩。赤霞珠在Perdeberg海拔较高的地点附近。</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>这款酒的起泡时间与以前的年份基本相同，平均每桶酿造约16个月，只有赤霞珠的部分会出现一些新橡木桶。该酒于今年6月下旬组装，进行了罚款和瓶装。在组装过程中，我们品尝了将近2400桶用于葡萄酒的酒，并仅选择了1 675桶作为最终葡萄酒。与我们2014年的产量水平相比略有下降。</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>品尝说明：</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>鼻子异常强烈且复杂，红色浆果果实与深色的果盘和Swartland紫罗兰并置。香气散发着覆盆子，桑,、黑莓，达姆森，黑巧克力和甘草的香气，还有几瓣丁香，肉豆蔻和橙皮。这款酒口感柔和顺滑，口感浓郁，酒体中带有丰富的红色和黑色浆果味</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>保持平衡的酸度和可可粉单宁。 Porseleinberg水果肯定会影响混合物，借贷结构和刺耳而又升华的香水。这款酒具有悠长而持久的风味，让人联想到瑞士黑榛子巧克力。</p>', '<p>我们在整个新西兰以及海外一些地区提供服务。 我们的送货是由我们自己和值得信赖的第三方快递员完成的。 有关价格和送货方式的更多详细信息，请转到我们网站的&ldquo;送货&rdquo;部分。</p>', NULL, '<p>The 2015 vintage, a blend of 71 % Syrah, 15% Grenache, 8% Cabernet Sauvignon, 5% Cinsault and a single percent of Viognier. A large component of the Syrah, Grenache and Cinsault is now coming off our own vineyards &ndash; the decomposed schists&rsquo; of Porseleinberg and Goldmine; the Cabernet Sauvignon off a higher altitude site in the Perdeberg.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>The &eacute;levage of the wine is much the same as in previous vintages, averaging about 16 months in barrique, with only the Cabernet Sauvignon fraction seeing some new oak. The wine was assembled in late June this year, fined and bottled. During the assemblage, we tasted nearly 2 400 barrels that were destined for the wine and selected only 1 675 barrels for the final wine. Slightly down from our 2014 production levels.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Tasting Notes:</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>The nose is exceptionally intense and complex with red berry fruit juxtaposed against a dark, brooding fruit compote and Swartland violets. The nose exudes aromas of raspberry, mulberry, blackberry, damson, dark chocolate, and licorice with whiffs of cloves, nutmeg, and orange rind. The wine has a soft, smooth entry, a rich mid-palate, and an abundance of red and blackberry fruit on the nose</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>follows through with balanced acidity and svelte cocoa powdery tannins. The Porseleinberg fruit certainly makes an impact to the blend, lending structure and a piercing yet lifted perfume. The wine has a long, lingering finish reminiscent of Swiss dark hazelnut chocolate.</p>', '<p>We deliver throughout New Zealand and to some locations overseas. Our deliveries are made by ourselves and trusted third party couriers. For further details on prices and delivery options please go to DELIVERY section of our website.</p>', 1, '', '2020-02-26 23:24:37', '2020-10-19 17:14:01'),
