('tLMW1582730670hkrp', 'file-manager/wine/替换图/2004DianaMadeline.jpg', '', '', 'Cullen Diana Madeline Cabernet Blend 2014', '', 168, '', 750, 13.5, 1, 1, 15, 1, 'AU', 14, 1, '[\"7\",\"8\",\"9\"]', NULL, NULL, 12, '2020-02-26', '2021-02-26', 0, 29, 1, 0, 0, 'Superb colour pouring a totally opaque black red with a bright dark crimson red black tinged hue. Exquisitely scented aromas of violets, blackcurrants and mulberries are infused with cedary tobacco characters with hints of black olive, spicy cigar box and faint bay leaf also present. Powerful, yet graceful and focused the palate is blessed with a rich core of fruit that includes blackcurrant, red currant and mulberry flavours.', '<p><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"color: #091d0c;\">Winemaker and environmentalist&nbsp;</span>Vanya Cullen<span style=\"color: #091d0c;\">, a strong believer in biodynamic viticulture, has harnessed the rhythms of the cosmos, Earth&rsquo;s energy and vitality to &lsquo;achieve greater individuality of site through working with nature rather than against it&rsquo;. In 1966 her parents Dr Kevin and Diana Cullen planted a trial one-acre (0.4-hectare) vineyard on their sheep and cattle property at Wilyabrup in the Margaret River.</span></span></p>', '<p>We deliver throughout New Zealand and to some locations overseas. Our deliveries are made by ourselves and trusted third party couriers. For further details on prices and delivery options please go to DELIVERY section of our website.</p>', 'Superb colour pouring a totally opaque black red with a bright dark crimson red black tinged hue. Exquisitely scented aromas of violets, blackcurrants and mulberries are infused with cedary tobacco characters with hints of black olive, spicy cigar box and faint bay leaf also present. Powerful, yet graceful and focused the palate is blessed with a rich core of fruit that includes blackcurrant, red currant and mulberry flavours.', '<p><span style=\"co