('UaGp1582730673CNPw', 'file-manager/NAISI/Lawson\'s chardonnay.png', 'file-manager/NAISI/Lawson\'s chardonnay.png', 'file-manager/NAISI/Lawson\'s chardonnay.png', 'Lawson\'s Dry Hills Estate Chardonnay 2018', 'Lawson\'s Dry Hills Estate Chardonnay 2018', 21, '', 750, 13, 2, 2, 2, 2, 'NZ', 20, 1, '[\"3\",\"4\",\"5\"]', NULL, NULL, 12, '2020-02-26', '2021-02-26', 0, 101, 1, 0, 0, '这款酒具有牛轧糖和柠檬的可爱香气，并带有蜂蜡和核果的香气。', '<p>一致性和可靠性是劳森的标志。 他们的霞多丽具有所有的作品（苹果酱，酒糟搅拌等），从而获得了奶油般的平衡口感，充满了核果和柑橘的香气。</p>', '<p>我们在整个新西兰以及海外一些地区提供服务。 我们的送货是由我们自己和值得信赖的第三方快递员完成的。 有关价格和送货方式的更多详细信息，请转到我们网站的&ldquo;送货&rdquo;部分。</p>', 'This wine has lovely aromas of nougat and lemon with notes of bees wax and stonefruits.', '<p><span style=\"font-family: Muli, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13.3333px;\">Consistency and reliability are the hallmarks of Lawson&rsquo;s. Their Chardonnay has had all the works (malo, lees stirring, etc.) with the result a creamy and balanced mouthful of stonefruit-and-citrus gorgeousness.</span></p>', '<p>We deliver throughout New Zealand and to some locations overseas. Our deliveries are made by ourselves and trusted third party couriers. For further details on prices and delivery options please go to DELIVERY section of our website.</p>', 1, '', '2020-02-26 23:24:33', '2020-10-19 17:01:04'),
