('VMOY1582730675RdmJ', 'file-manager/wine/Muriel.png', '', '', 'Bodegas Muriel Rioja Crianza', 'Bodegas Muriel Rioja Crianza', 26, '', 750, 14, 1, 1, 34, 1, 'ES', 29, 2, '[\"7\",\"8\",\"9\"]', NULL, NULL, 12, '2020-02-26', '2021-02-26', 0, 137, 1, 0, 0, 'Bodegas Muriel是Murua家族拥有的四个酿酒厂之一，该家族有85年的葡萄酒经销历史', '<p>Bodegas Muriel是Murua家族拥有的四个酿酒厂之一，Murua家族从事葡萄酒的历史可追溯到85年，这使它们成为Rioja相对年轻的枪支！确实，直到1986年，才建立了现有的杂货店，现在不仅通过购买葡萄园来生产葡萄酒，而且在家族经营葡萄酒的同时也建立了必要的合同种植者关系。</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>这款酒果味甜美，同时美味可口，散发着五香的樱桃，李子，黑蘑菇和烤杏仁的香气，散发出淡淡的烟熏味和花香。口感多汁，美味，提供多汁的水果风味，以及多汁，咸味的口感，细腻的口感和光洁的单宁完美地衬托出这种口感。喝到2020年;评分：92分；山姆&middot;金；葡萄酒轨道</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>红色水果，香料，香草和椰子。酒体中等，红色，带有一层香草饼干橡木，柔软的单宁，也许有些香肠味，以及带有粉质单宁的干净表面。做得好。你得到你想要的。酒精度：13.5％；价钱：$ 24;饮料：2018-2020 +;评分：90分；加里&middot;沃尔什；葡萄酒前线</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>它有鲜红色的樱桃和浆果，略带泥土味。口感中等，果味顺滑，单宁成熟。现在喝。评分：90分；詹姆斯&middot;萨克林</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>这款深红色的酒带有一束非常芬芳的香气，例如融合了雪松和薄荷的黑莓果酱，其味道充满了李子，樱桃，香料和甘草精，以及香兰橡木，甚至还有一点烟草味。口感柔滑，单宁柔滑，肉质浓郁，略带焦油味，余味悠长，多汁且美味。 Sue Courntey，wineoftheweek.com</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>成熟浆果的泥土香气与辛辣橡木和香草的香气完美融合。口感活泼，酸度明亮，散发出五香李子，番茄，红醋栗和干土的味道。这是经典的里奥哈（Rioja）薄脆饼，在接下来的几年中将是诚实，新鲜和可饮用的。葡萄酒爱好者</p>', '<p>我们在整个新西兰以及海外一些地区提供服务。 我们的送货是由我们自己和值得信赖的第三方快递员完成的。 有关价格和送货方式的更多详细信息，请转到我们网站的&ldquo;送货&rdquo;部分。</p>', 'Bodegas Muriel is one of four wineries owned by the Murua Family which has a history of dealing in wine dating back 85 years', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: rubik, sans-serif; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 0px 0px 10px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; color: #333333;\">Bodegas Muriel is one of four wineries owned by the Murua Family which has a history of dealing in wine dating back 85 years - making them a relative young gun in Rioja! Indeed it was only in 1986 that the existing bodega was established and production is now made from both purchased vineyards as well as imperative contract grower relationships forged all the while the family dealt in wine.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: rubik, sans-serif; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 0px 0px 10px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; color: #333333;\">Sweetly fruited and richly savoury at the same time, the wine shows lifted aromas of spiced cherry, plum, dark mushroom and toasted almond characters with nuances of smoked game and floral. The palate is juicy and flavoursome, delivering succulent fruit flavours together with meaty, savoury undertones, wonderfully framed by fine texture and polished tannins. Drink to 2020; Rating: 92 Points; Sam Kim; Wine Orbit</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: rubik, sans-serif; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 0px 0px 10px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; color: #333333;\">Red fruit, spice, vanilla and coconut. Medium-bodied, red fruits with a layer of vanilla biscuit oak, supple tannin, perhaps some sausage savouries, and a clean finish with silty tannin cleaning up. Good job. You get what you came for. Alcohol: 13.5%; Price: $24; Drink: 2018-2020+; Rating: 90 Points; Gary Walsh; The Wine Front</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: rubik, sans-serif; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 0px 0px 10px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; color: #333333;\">This has bright red cherries and berries and gently earthy complexity. The palate has medium body and smoothly arranged fruit with nutty, ripe tannins. Drink now. Rating: 90 Points; James Suckling</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: rubik, sans-serif; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 0px 0px 10px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; color: #333333;\">This deep dark red-hued wine has a wonderfully fragrant bouquet like blackberry jam infused with cedar and mint and the flavours are crammed with plums, cherries, spice and liquorice with sappy vanillin oak and perhaps a hint of tobacco. It&rsquo;s bright in the mouth with silky tannins, a meaty richness and an underlying tarry savouriness and the lingering finish is long, juicy and flavoursome. Sue Courntey, wineoftheweek.com</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: rubik, sans-serif; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 0px 0px 10px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; color: #333333;\">Earthy aromas of ripe berry fruits blend well with spicy oak and vanilla notes. A lively palate with bright acidity puts out flavors of spiced plum, tomato, red currant and dried earth. This is a classic Rioja crianza that\'s honest, fresh and eminently drinkable over the next few years. Wine Enthusiast</p>', '<p>We deliver throughout New Zealand and to some locations overseas. Our deliveries are made by ourselves and trusted third party couriers. For further details on prices and delivery options please go to DELIVERY section of our website.</p>', 1, '', '2020-02-26 23:24:35', '2020-10-19 18:19:51'),
('vSJT1582730674ViiR', 'file-manager/wine/Rose mondillo f.png', '', '', 'Mondillo Rose 2019', '', 27, '', 750, 13, 1, 6, 4, 3, 'NZ', 9, 1, '[\"3\",\"4\",\"5\",\"7\"]', NULL, NULL, 12, '2020-02-26', '2021-02-26', 0, 130, 1, 0, 0, NULL, '<p>带有草莓，覆盆子和西瓜的香气，结合樱桃干的清爽口感。</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>MondilloRos&eacute;产自100％黑比诺葡萄，这些葡萄来自专门为我们的Ros&eacute;种植的葡萄园。 选择的单个克隆可提供这种酒红色的水果风味，并具有中等的甜度和水果甜度。 留在皮肤上几天，以建立鲜明的粉红色。</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>2020年中奥塔哥中部的生长季节始于凉爽的春天，随后是温暖的夏天，夏季果实集中但产量低。 蒙迪洛&middot;罗斯（MondilloRos&eacute;）葡萄于2020年4月手工收获。</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>酒窖：即日起至2024年</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>非常适合在夏季举行的任何活动，庆典或晚餐聚会。 搭配沙拉，烤虾，鲑鱼，意大利调味饭，甜瓜和意大利熏火腿！ 服务冷藏。</p>', '<p>我们在整个新西兰以及海外一些地区提供服务。 我们的送货是由我们自己和值得信赖的第三方快递员完成的。 有关价格和送货方式的更多详细信息，请转到我们网站的&ldquo;送货&rdquo;部分。</p>', NULL, '<p>A lusciously refreshing wine with aromas of strawberry, raspberry and watermelon combined with a cherry dry finish.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Mondillo Ros&eacute; is produced from 100% Pinot Noir grapes from a defined parcel of the vineyard grown specifically for our Ros&eacute;. The single clone selected offers this wine red fruit flavours with a mid-palate lusciousness and fruit sweetness. Left on the skins for a few days to establish the vibrant cerise-pink colour.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>The 2020 Central Otago growing season started off with a cool spring, followed by a warm summer which produced concentrated fruit but low yields. Mondillo Ros&eacute; grapes were hand harvested in April 2020.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Drink/Cellar: Now until 2024</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Perfect for any event, celebration or dinner party over the summer months. Enjoy with salads, grilled prawns, salmon, risotto, rock melon &amp; prosciutto! Serve chilled.</p>', '<p>We deliver throughout New Zealand and to some locations overseas. Our deliveries are made by ourselves and trusted third party couriers. For further details on prices and delivery options please go to DELIVERY section of our website.</p>', 1, '', '2020-02-26 23:24:34', '2020-10-21 12:10:39'),
('VtuU1582730675mcno', 'file-manager/M1.png', '', '', 'Pegasus Bay Riesling 2016', 'Pegasus Bay Riesling 2016', 33, '', 750, 12.5, 2, 2, 22, 2, 'NZ', 30, 1, '[\"3\",\"5\",\"7\",\"10\"]', NULL, NULL, 12, '2020-02-26', '2021-02-26', 0, 147, 1, 0, 0, '夏季温暖，夜晚凉爽，土壤多石且播种水平低是雷司令生产的理想条件！ 异国风味，上等酸和微妙的甜味以绝对和谐的方式融合在一起，难怪它一直受到追捧。', '<p>Pegasus Bay Riesling无疑是使Waipara出现在地图上的葡萄酒。 这是经典之作，始终如一。 在一天中的任何时候都完美无缺-它会让您感觉良好。</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&ldquo;开花期间的温暖和稳定的天气导致了非常大的初期结实。然后进行了疏果工作，使农作物恢复到理想的水平。一个完美的夏天，接着是温暖干燥的秋天，使得随后的葡萄能够收获并具有出色的风味发展 颜色是柠檬秸秆。在鼻子上有很多柑橘，尤其是定义北坎特伯雷司令的橙皮，还有淡淡的苹果和杏红，并带有金银花和番石榴。 延长的悬挂时间增加了口感的浓度，并赋予了结构和长度的成熟酚醛成分。尽管其酒体香醇，但其酸度仍保持清爽爽口，与干爽的口感完美匹配。&rdquo;</p>', '<p>We deliver throughout New Zealand and to some locations overseas. Our deliveries are made by ourselves and trusted third party couriers. For further details on prices and delivery options please go to DELIVERY section of our website.</p>', 'Warm summer days, cool nights, stony soils and low cropping levels are perfect conditions for Riesling production! Exotic flavours, fine acids and delicate sweetness in absolute harmony, little wonder it\'s perennially sought after.', '<p>Pegasus Bay Riesling is arguably the wine that put Waipara on the map. It\'s a classic and always delivers. Perfect at any time of the day - it just makes you feel good.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>\"Warm and settled weather during flowering led to a very large initial set. Fruit thinning was then undertaken to bring the crop back to the desired level. A perfect summer, followed by warm dry autumn enabled the subsequent grapes to be harvested with excellent flavour development and physiological ripeness. The colour is lemon-straw. On the nose, there is an abundance of citrus, particularly the orange zest that so defines North Canterbury Rieslings. There are also hints of red apple and apricot, layered with honeysuckle and guava. The extended hang time has added concentration to the palate, together with ripe phenolics that give structure and length. Despite its body, the wine still has a crisp and refreshing acidity that matches its off-dry finish perfectly.\"&nbsp;</p>', NULL, 1, '', '2020-02-26 23:24:35', '2020-09-10 09:06:41'),
