('WrIJ1582730676zQLO', 'file-manager/wine/wine brand/002.png', '', '', '黑桃橡木 Vigneron Syrah 2013', 'Spade Oak Vigneron Syrah 2013', 37, '', 750, 13.5, 1, 1, 8, 1, 'NZ', 1, 1, '[\"7\",\"8\",\"9\"]', NULL, NULL, 12, '2020-02-26', '2021-02-26', 0, 162, 1, 0, 0, '来自新西兰吉斯本地区的西拉', '<p>这款酒色泽诱浓厚，诱人甜美，口感柔软如天鹅绒，每一次都超载。充满深色奇异水果，香料，白胡椒和黑胡椒香，略带巧克力味，甚至还有一阵鲜花。 Spade Oak Vigneron Syrah干燥，结实且结构奇妙，在接下来的五到十年内将完全陈年。</p>', '<p>我们在整个新西兰以及海外一些地区提供服务。 我们的送货是由我们自己和值得信赖的第三方快递员完成的。 有关价格和送货方式的更多详细信息，请转到我们网站的&ldquo;送货&rdquo;部分。</p>', 'Syrah from Gisborne, New Zealand', '<p>Deep and tempting in color and luscious, and soft as velvet in the mouth, this is a wine that over-delivers every time. Perfumed with dark exotic fruits, spice, white and black pepper and just a touch of chocolaty goodness, and even a whiff of flowers. The dry, firm, and wonderfully structured, Spade Oak Vigneron Syrah will age perfectly over the next five to ten years.</p>', '<p>We deliver throughout New Zealand and to some locations overseas. Our deliveries are made by ourselves and trusted third party couriers. For further details on prices and delivery options please go to DELIVERY section of our website.</p>', 1, '', '2020-02-26 23:24:36', '2020-09-03 13:19:25'),
