(45, 'Muscat', NULL, '霞多麗是世界上最著名和廣泛種植的白色品種。儘管霞多麗以獨特的風格引起人們的熱愛或憎恨而享譽盛名，但實際上，霞多麗還是最中立的白人之一。儘管質地很重，但蘋果，核果和柑桔的柔和味道實際上使其他元素發光。霞多麗是新世界風格的黃油和烤麵包橡木味的理想之選，同樣適用於法國勃艮第的原始住宅，在更細，更精緻的例子中，相同的中性使其可以揭示土壤，葡萄園和土壤的細微差別。年份。', 'Chardonnay is the world’s most famous and widely planted white variety. Despite a reputation for distinctive styles that inspire love or hate, Chardonnay is in fact one of the most neutral whites. Though weighty in texture its gentle flavours of apple, stone fruit and citrus in effect allow other elements to shine. A perfect vehicle for the butter and toasty oak flavours of the New World style, Chardonnay is equally suited to its original home in France’s Burgundy, where in much leaner and finer examples the same neutrality permits it to reveal the subtlest nuances of soil, vineyard and vintage.', 'file-manager\\wine\\chardonnay.jpg', 1, 1, 1, '2020-02-26 23:24:37', '2020-04-11 10:41:43');

